- cs.LG (Machine Learning): Although the paper does not explicitly mention machine learning, the use of optimization techniques and the focus on finding an optimal solution to a coordination problem may be relevant to the machine learning community.
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The paper deals with distributed control design, which is a key area of research in distributed computing.
- cs.OH (Other Computer Science): This paper may also be classified under the "Other Computer Science" category, as it does not fit neatly into any of the other categories and covers a broad range of topics related to control design and coordination in multi-agent systems.
